import React from 'react'

const InfoSection = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <InfoContainer id={id}>
            <InfoWrapper>
                <InfoRow>
                    <Column1>
                    <TextWrapper>
                        <TopLine>TopLine</TopLine>
                        <Heading>Heading</Heading>
                        <Subtitle>Subtitle</Subtitle>
                        <BtnWrap>
                            <Button to='home'>Button</Button>
                        </BtnWrap>
                    </TextWrapper>
                    </Column1>
                </InfoRow>
            </InfoWrapper>
        </InfoContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default InfoSection
